Reproducible: Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Launch orca, enable orca speech.
2. Launch thunderbird, set up an account.
3. Select &quot;File&quot;-&gt;&quot;Page Setup...&quot; to open the &quot;Page Setup&quot; window.
4. Using &quot;tab&quot; to navigate the window.
Actual Results:  
When focus on the radio button &quot;Portrait&quot;, orca will says &quot;Portrait&quot;.

Expected Results:  
Orca says &quot;selected item&quot; instead.</thetext>
